snippet.textDisplay: Assalatu wassalamu Alaika Ya Sayyidina wa Maulana Muhammad Mustafa Ahmad Mustafa SAAS Unjurna Madad Nazar Karam.Assalatu wassalamu Alaika Ya Ummul Mumineen Hazrat Khadija Tul Kubra RA Salamullah ta'ala Alika unjurna,Madad, Nazar Karam. Assalatu Wassalamu Alaika Ya Ahle Bait RA Salamullah ta'ala Alaikum unjurna Madad Nazar Karam.Assalatu wassalamu Alaika Ya Bente Sayyidina wa Maulana Muhammad Mustafa SAAS Ahmad Mustafa SAAS sayyidina wa Maulana MuhammadurRasulUllah SAAS Syeda Kainat Syeda Fatima Zahra R A Salamullah Taala Alaika unjurna,Madad, Nazar Karam.Assalatu wassalamu Alaika Ya Ahle Bait R A Salamullah Taala Alaika unjurna, Madad, Nazar Karam. Assalatu wassalamu Alaika ya bente Syeda Kainat Syeda Fatima Zahra R A Salamullah Taala Alaika Syeda Zainab RA Salamullah taala Alaika unjurna, Madad, Nazar Karam.Assalatu Wassalamu Alaikum ya Tamam Imam Awlade Ahle Bait RA Salam Allah Taala Alaikum. Assalatu Wassalamu Alaika Ya Awlad E Ahle Bait RA Salamullah Taala Alaika Hazrat Imam Ali Raza RA .Salamullah Taala Alaikum unjurna , Madad, Nazar Karam. .Ya Allah Ya Rasool Allah SAAS bless us, forgive us and guide us in every moment in this world and in the world hereafter Ameen Summa Amen. Allahumma Salli Ala Sayyidina wa Maulana Muhammadin wa ala Ale sayyidina wa Maulana Muhammadin Afzala Salawateqa wa Barack wa sallam Alaihe Ameen Summa Ameen. SubhanAllah Alhamdulillah Allahuakbar wa La ilaha Illallah Muhammadur RasulUllah SAAS. Subhanallahi wa Bihamdihi subhanAllahil Azeem wa Bihamdihi Astaghfirullah. Rabbana Atina fid dunya hasanah wa fil Akhirati Hasanah waqina adzabannar. Ameen. Summa Ameen La ilaha Illa Anta Nuraiyahdi ya Allahu Binurihi maia shau Mohammadur Rasool Allah SAAS Imamul Mursalin wa Khatamun Nabiyeen SAAS.May Allah RasulUllah SAAS bless us, forgive us and guide us in every moment.Ameen.Assalatu wassalamu Alaikum Ya Gausul Azam Dastageer ya Bara Peer shaheb  Hassani Hussaini Syed Ya Sheikh Hazrat Abdul Qadir Jilani RA shaian Lillahi Taala unjurna ,Madad. Nazar Karam.
